# Installation of GHC 7.10.3

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution  
cd $HOME/Downloads  

wget https://www.haskell.org/ghc/dist/7.10.3/ghc-7.10.3-i386-deb8-linux.tar.bz2
tar xvfj ghc-7.10.3-i386-deb8-linux.tar.bz2
cd ghc-7.10.3  

# install to  
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-7.10.3  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-7.10.3  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd $HOME/Downloads  
rm -rfv ghc-7.10.3*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
switchghc 7.10.3 
~~~